INSTALLATION

Opera users go here: https://addons.opera.com/it/extensions/details/facebook-adless/?display=en

Firefox users:
1) Install Greasemonkey: https://addons.mozilla.org/it/firefox/addon/greasemonkey/
2) go here: https://github.com/frankdd89/Facebook-adless/downloads

Chrome users:
1) Download Javascript here: https://github.com/frankdd89/Facebook-adless/downloads
2) Go to Settings->Extensions and drag and drop in the javascript you have just downloaded
